But this is not the marriage, it is the divorce stage.  Lines have
been drawn, the woman and man have gone their separate ways, and the
children have been placed in the custody by order of the court.

This is not a 'why should I' as much as it is a 'okay, you did not
carefully budget your money - what does that have to do with me?'.  If
